org.modelio.api.module.command.standard

Class RunJythonScriptStandardHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.api.module.command.DefaultModuleCommandHandler
      • org.modelio.api.module.command.standard.RunJythonScriptBasicHandler
        • org.modelio.api.module.command.standard.RunJythonScriptStandardHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModuleCommandHandler

    public class RunJythonScriptStandardHandler
extends RunJythonScriptBasicHandler
    Command handler that runs a Jython script.

    The jython script must be in the SCRIPT_PARAM command parameter.

    Used parameters:

    • "accept" : Jython script called by accept(List, IModule)
    • "isActiveFor" : Jython script called by isActiveFor(List, IModule)

    The scripts are run with the bindings configured by RunJythonScriptBasicHandler.configure(ScriptEngine, List, IModule).

    Since:
    3.4
